OL,3,CChild rapist jailed for second time
OL,4,Cover attack on teenage girl
OL,6,FThe girl refused, but Hussain, who was
OL,7,Falso aged around 14 at the time, raped
OL,8,Fher.
OL,10,FThe 40-year-old offender was already
OL,11,Fserving a 19-year sentence for the
OL,12,Frape of another girl when he was given
OL,13,Fanother three-year sentence at
OL,14,FSheffield Crown Court on Tuesday,
OL,15,Fwhich he will serve concurrently.
OL,17,FRevelations of his offending came
OL,18,Fabout as a result of the National
OL,19,FCrime Agency's Operation Stovewood,
OL,20,Finvestigating child sexual
OL,21,Fexploitation in the town.
