OL,6,FHussain's victim in this offence had
OL,7,Fcome forward identifying herself as
OL,8,Fhaving been sexually abused as a
OL,9,Fchild. She told officers Hussain had
OL,10,Fattacked her in an alleyway, with a
OL,11,Fsubsequent investigation backing up
OL,12,Fher story.
OL,14,FThe child rapist was charged in
OL,15,FFebruary last year while in prison,
OL,16,Fbefore being convicted after trial
OL,17,Falongside two other men for offences
OL,18,Fagainst a different girl.
