OL,6,FNCA senior investigating officer Alan
OL,7,FHastings said: "The victim has shown
OL,8,Fenormous strength and fortitude in
OL,9,Freporting what Sageer Hussain did to
OL,10,Fher.
OL,12,F"The woman bravely told officers about
OL,13,FHussain's horrific crime against her,
OL,14,Fand that significantly helped our
OL,15,Finvestigation. Officers subsequently
OL,16,Fidentified corroborating evidence that
OL,17,Fenabled us to secure justice for the
OL,18,Fwoman. Hussain, who is already serving
OL,19,Ftime for raping another girl, will now
OL,20,Fremain in prison for longer.
